      "content": "i mean, if it's all just a temporary glitch and there's no real purpose to the struggle, it almost feels like it would be more logical to just opt out early. why stay in the cycle of pain if the end result is the same anyway? it seems like the only way to actually find some peace is to just be done with it.",
